                <h2 class="section-title">Scheme Design – Free Cover Limit, Membership, and Tax Treatment</h2>

                <h3 class="section-subtitle">Actively at Work Clause</h3>
                <p class="intro">Members must be actively at work on the date of scheme commencement to be covered from that date. An employee absent due to illness on the scheme commencement date will not be covered until they return to active employment.</p>

                <h3 class="section-subtitle">Tax Treatment Summary</h3>

